# Canonical host redirect: www -> non-www (301). Cloudflare Pages supports
# absolute-URL sources in _redirects for host normalisation.
https://www.izmirshoreexcursions.com/*  https://izmirshoreexcursions.com/:splat  301!
http://www.izmirshoreexcursions.com/*   https://izmirshoreexcursions.com/:splat  301!

# HTTP -> HTTPS on the apex is handled automatically by Cloudflare
# ("Always Use HTTPS"). Kept here as a defensive fallback.
http://izmirshoreexcursions.com/*       https://izmirshoreexcursions.com/:splat  301!
